kind: cattle and creeping things and beasts of the earth after their kind\"; and it was so."}, {:version=>"New King James Version", :text=>"Then God said, “Let the earth bring forth the living creature according to its kind: cattle and creeping thing and beast of the earth, "}, {:version=>" according to its kind”; and it was so.", :text=>"King James Bible"}, {:version=>"And God said, Let the earth bring forth the living creature after his kind, cattle, and creeping thing, and beast of the earth after his kind: and it was so.", :text=>"Christian Standard Bible"}, {:version=>"Then God said, \"Let the earth produce living creatures according to their kinds: livestock, creatures that crawl, and the wildlife of the earth according to their kinds.\" And it was so.", :text=>"Contemporary English Version"}, {:version=>"God said, \"I command the earth to give life to all kinds of tame animals, wild animals, and reptiles.\" And that's what happened. ", :text=>"Good News Translation"}, {:version=>"Then God commanded, \"Let the earth produce all kinds of animal life: domestic and wild, large and small\"--and it was done. ", :text=>"Holman Christian Standard Bible"}, {:version=>"Then God said, \"Let the earth produce living creatures according to their kinds: livestock, creatures that crawl, and the wildlife of the earth according to their kinds.\" And it was so. ", :text=>"International Standard Version"}, {:version=>"Then God said, \"Let the earth bring forth each kind of living creature, each kind of livestock and crawling thing, and each kind of earth's animals!\" And that is what happened:", :text=>"NET Bible"}, {:version=>"God said, \"Let the land produce living creatures according to their kinds: cattle, creeping things, and wild animals, each according to its kind.\" It was so.", :text=>"New Heart English Bible"}, {:version=>"And God said, \"Let the earth bring forth living creatures after its kind: tame animals, and crawling creatures, and wild animals of the earth after its kind.\" And it was so. ", :text=>"GOD'S WORD® Translation"}, {:version=>"Then God said, \"Let the earth produce every type of living creature: every type of domestic animal, crawling animal, and wild animal.\" And so it was.", :text=>"JPS Tanakh 1917"}, {:version=>"And God said: 'Let the earth bring forth the living creature after its kind, cattle, and creeping thing, and beast of the earth after its kind.' And it was so.", :text=>"New American Standard 1977 "}, {:version=>"Then God said, “Let the earth bring forth living creatures after their kind: cattle and creeping things and beasts of the earth after their kind”; and it was so.", :text=>"King James 2000 Bible"}, {:version=>"And God said, Let the earth bring forth living creatures after their kinds, cattle, and creeping things, and beasts of the earth after their kinds: and it was so", :text=>"American King James Version"}, {:version=>"And God said, Let the earth bring forth the living creature after his kind, cattle, and creeping thing, and beast of the earth after his kind: and it was so.", :text=>"American Standard Version"}, {:version=>"And God said, Let the earth bring forth living creatures after their kind, cattle, and creeping things, and beasts of the earth after their kind: and it was so.", :text=>"Brenton Septuagint Translation"}, {:version=>"And God said, Let the earth bring forth the living creature according to its kind, quadrupeds and reptiles and wild beasts of the earth according to their kind, and it was so.", :text=>"Douay-Rheims Bible"}, {:version=>"And God said: Let the earth bring forth the living creature in its kind, cattle and creeping things, and beasts of the earth, according to their kinds. And it was so done. ", :text=>"Darby Bible Translation"}, {:version=>"And God said, Let the earth bring forth living souls after their kind, cattle, and creeping thing, and beast of the earth, after their kind. And it was so.", :text=>"English Revised Version"}, {:version=>"And God said, Let the earth bring forth the living creature after its kind, cattle, and creeping thing, and beast of the earth after its kind: and it was so.", :text=>"Webster's Bible Translation"}, {:version=>"And God said, Let the earth bring forth the living creature after his kind, cattle, and the creeping animal, and the beast of the earth after his kind: and it was so.", :text=>"World English Bible"}, {:version=>"God said, \"Let the earth bring forth living creatures after their kind, livestock, creeping things, and animals of the earth after their kind;\" and it was so.", :text=>"Young's Literal Translation"}, {:version=>" And God saith, 'Let the earth bring forth the living creature after its kind, cattle and creeping thing, and beast of the earth after its kind:' and it is so.", :text=>nil}]}